{"type": "article", "id": 22517, "title": "折叠砧板", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-19T07:10:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021339021ToIaDBUPyVw3edW.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款折叠砧板，以方便将切好的菜倒进锅内。它的原理其实很简单，使用两块同样大小的木板，在侧面装上钢夹。它也有拍压一些菜的功能。也许对于小厨房来说，一个折叠的砧板也是一个节约空间的办法。有 3 种深浅颜色可选，售价 42 美元起，<a href=\"http://shop.stumpfstudio.com/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133900mbef82EXiQN3tUTY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133900Exq3FfouUg0YG6an.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133901s9ywtXZcr3j8obk7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133901JtzGIvq140sEAKVW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}